snippet.title: Paani Ch Madhaani (Trailer) | Gippy Grewal | Neeru Bajwa | Gurpreet Ghuggi | Iftikhar Thakur |
snippet.description:
Movie Starcast  - Gippy Grewal,Neeru Bajwa,Gurpreet Ghuggi,Karamjit Anmol,Iftikhar Thakur,Harby Sangha,Rupinder Rupi,Shivam Sharma, Honey Mattu,Parveen Aawara.

Director - Vijay Kumar Arora
Written By - Naresh Kathooria
Dop - Jailesh Oberoi
Editor - Bunty Nagi
Music - Jatinder Shah
Singer - Gippy Grewal,Afsana Khan,Ranjit Bawa,Jasbir Jassi
Lyrics - Happy Raikoti
Background score : Samdeep Saxena. 
Assistant Programming: Pankaj Birha. 
Flute : Pankaj Nath. 
Violin : Kailash Patra. 
Guitars : Akash
Vocals : Moumeeta 
Sound Engineer: Bhanu Thakur.
Produced By - Sunny Raj, Dr. Prabhjot S Sidhu( Seattle, Usa), Mani Dhaliwal
Executive Producer - Gurpreet Singh Goga
Worldwide Distribution- Omjee Star Studios
Pr & Marketing - Prinday
